@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Sakura MK I Credit Card BIN Data Service - Control Flow

actor "External Client" as Client
participant "API Gateway" as API
participant "S3" as S3
participant "CSV Ingestion\nLambda" as IngestLambda
participant "SQS/Kinesis" as Queue
participant "Message Splitter\nLambda" as SplitterLambda
participant "Data Transformation\nLambda" as TransformLambda
participant "DynamoDB" as DynamoDB

== Data Ingestion Flow ==

Client -> API: POST /upload BIN CSV
activate API
API -> S3: Store CSV file
activate S3
S3 --> API: File stored (S3 Event)
deactivate S3

API -> IngestLambda: Trigger (S3 Event)
activate IngestLambda
IngestLambda -> S3: Read CSV file
activate S3
S3 --> IngestLambda: CSV data
deactivate S3

IngestLambda -> IngestLambda: Parse CSV records
IngestLambda -> Queue: Send BIN records as messages
activate Queue
Queue --> IngestLambda: Messages queued
IngestLambda --> API: Ingestion complete
deactivate IngestLambda
API --> Client: 200 OK
deactivate API

== Message Processing Flow ==

Queue -> SplitterLambda: Trigger (New messages)
activate SplitterLambda
SplitterLambda -> Queue: Poll messages
Queue --> SplitterLambda: BIN record messages
deactivate Queue

SplitterLambda -> SplitterLambda: Split and validate records

SplitterLambda -> Queue: Send split messages
activate Queue
Queue --> SplitterLambda: Messages queued
deactivate SplitterLambda
deactivate Queue

Queue -> TransformLambda: Trigger (New messages)
activate TransformLambda
TransformLambda -> Queue: Poll messages
activate Queue
Queue --> TransformLambda: BIN data messages
deactivate Queue

TransformLambda -> TransformLambda: Transform BIN data
TransformLambda -> DynamoDB: Store processed BIN data
activate DynamoDB
DynamoDB --> TransformLambda: Write confirmation
deactivate DynamoDB
deactivate TransformLambda

== Query Flow ==

Client -> API: GET /bin/{binNumber}
activate API
API -> TransformLambda: Query BIN data
activate TransformLambda
TransformLambda -> DynamoDB: Query by BIN number
activate DynamoDB
DynamoDB --> TransformLambda: BIN data
deactivate DynamoDB
TransformLambda --> API: BIN information
deactivate TransformLambda
API --> Client: 200 OK (BIN details)
deactivate API

@enduml
